- man page, internal documentation
- rotation support
- support for more graphics formats
- image_convert: cspace, depth, scale
- image_info: inverted grayscale
- tiff: tiled, indexed, jpeg, raw jpeg/lzw/ccitt
- gif: data reading, compression, color space, and depth detection
- force specific color space / depth
- force portrait/landscape/bbox
- specify paper size as pair of dimens
- supply colorimage emulation for level1 (rgb-8 done)
- masking (1-bit alpha channel)
- preview
- (optional) language level check in PostScript code
- more regression tests

+ indexed png to grayscale conversion segfaults in libpng
+ depth 12 requires level 2
